Author: needmoney
Title: [BOUNTY] TIPPER ECONOMY -> BOUNTY OVER, PLEASE READ.
Body: Hello everyone, we are locking the thread to prevent cheaters from adding reports to their previous messages.  You can contact us directly from Telegram regarding any problem and we will solve it.  @TokenSuiteBuse    PLEASE ONLY USE BOUNTY THREAD FOR SUPPORT.     At first, there was the birth of the social network, now the world will experience the birth of the social economy. Tipper is the revolutionary decentralized social media platform founded on tipping, a game-changing paradigm shift that brings unlimited monetization for all users, and hails the end of view fraud, demonetization and censorship. "Likes", "votes", and "views" box everyone into the same level of expression, but tips are boundless due to human diversity, opening a Pandora's Box of unprecedented monetization for the world. For the first time ever, tipping is now incentivized through the four revolutionary monetization features (pillars) of two-way Tipping, Content Investing, Momentization and Branded Tips. The Tipper Blockchain performs at 250K+ micro-transactions/s, bringing the world monetized video-decentralization on a Facebook and YouTube scale, through Tipper's revolutionary technological leap of transaction mining.  Game changing Social Media Platform for the Growing Patron Generation. Where Tipping Pays.  Website | Whitepaper | Twitter | Facebook | Telegram   This bounty campaign will last for 3 weeks. Tipper Economy team is offering 1 500 000 Tokens which are equal to $375 000.  Click here to go INVEST!  The ICO is live!  Bounty Allocation  Signature Bounty 25% - 375 000 Tokens Translation 15% - 225 000 Tokens Youtube/Blogging Bounty 20% - 300 000 Tokens Facebook Bounty 15% - 225 000 Tokens Twitter Bounty 15% - 225 000 Tokens Telegram Bounty 10% - 150 000 Tokens  General Rules  Signature stakes will be distributed every week, other stakes will be calculated end of the campaign. First week of the bounty campaign will start on 8th of March, Monday. For any questions regarding the bounty campaign, you can contact me through PM, write a post to this thread. We reserve our right to eliminate you if we think you haven't been honest with your work. We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules. Please use this thread for bounty related questions (rank up, address change etc.). Do not PM us.   Signature Campaign   Weekly Rewards:  Jr. Member: 0,50 stake per week Member: 0,75 stake per week Full Member: 1 stake per week (+0.25 stake for avatar) Senior Member: 1,5 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar) Hero Member: 2 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar) Legendary: 2,25 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar)   Signature Campaign Rules:  Participants have to be at least Jr. Member. Every participants must wear our signature and personal text. Multiple accounts will be banned if spotted. Spam is not allowed. We expect you to post 10 constructive posts per week. Only 3 of these posts can be in local boards. You have to spread your posts through the days in a week. We will not count posts made in a single day. Posts should be made in altcoin sections, local board included (excluding bounties sections). You will have to keep wearing our signature, avatar and personal text until the end of the second round. Do not fill the form without wearing our signature, or you will be rejected. We will single handedly check every post of every participant. If we think you even had a single low effort post, you will be given 0 stakes that week. Posts should be spread through weeks. We don’t accept posts that are made in a single day.   Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s  Avatar, personal text and signature codes are on the second post of this thread.   Youtube/Blogging/Article Campaign   You will have to apply to us with your Youtube channel before start working. Youtube videos must be at least 2 minutes long. You must have at least 200 organic subscribers. You should have links to our website and whitepaper. Your Medium/Steem.it or any other free blogging blog page should have at least 50 followers. Your article must be original and contain at least 500 words. You should have links to our website and whitepaper. We also accept ICO Rating - Listing websites. This is a high quality project, and we encourage genuine discussion and opinions.  Any misrepresentations of the project/ false claims will not be permitted and stakes will not be awarded. You will get stakes based on the quality and popularity of your work, reviewed at the end of the campaign.   Spreadsheet of accepted works: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s    Twitter Campaign   All participants must follow our official Twitter account. Your audit score must be more than 90%. We will check every participant to make sure their Twitter account is genuine. Your Twitter account must be mainly about cryptocurrencies, real estate or investments. We will also accept media personalities. You have to have at least 100 real followers. Everyone has to report their custom Tweets and Likes every week. You can report max 3 Retweets and Likes per week. To help with this, we will add dates on the Twitter spreadsheet on weeks.  Stakes: (stakes double if you have more than 10 000 followers)  We will accept anyone with more than %90 audit score.  If you have more than 1000 followers you'll get:  - 0.5 stake for retweeting - 0.5 stake for like  If you have less than 1000 followers you'll get:  - 0.25 stake for retweeting - 0.25 stake for like  2 costum tweets per user for a single week.  Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s    Facebook Campaign   All participants must follow and like our Official Facebook Page. We will check every participant to make sure their Facebook account is genuine. Your Facebook account must be real. We don’t accept fake accounts. You have to have at least 100 real followers/friends. Everyone has to report their Shares and Likes. Maximum 1 Share&Like in a day, 5 Shares&Likes in a week. Do not create a new post for report. Edit your first post if you can. To help with this, we will add dates on the Facebook spreadsheet on weeks.  Stakes: (stakes double if you have more than 10 000 followers)  If you have more than 1000 friends you'll get: - weekly 0.5 stake for like - weekly 0.5 stake for share  If you have less than 1000 friends you'll get: - weekly 0.25 stake for like - weekly 0.25 stake for share  Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s      Translation Campaign   We will ask you to translate our ANN and WP. We expect text to be written and proofread by humans, if we find out you've used automation tools to provide the translation (e.g. Google Translate), you will be banned from the campaign as a whole. If we find out you've used Google Translate, you will be banned from the campaign as a whole. You are expected to moderate and update your thread with our news and updates to our ANN thread, at least once a week. You are expected to finish ANN and Bounty translation in 2 days (7 days for WP) after you've assigned with the job. We only limited number of languages, they will be selected from the most active communities on Bitcointalk. ANN and Bounty Thread translation will earn you 10 stakes and WP 100 stakes. At the end of the campaign we will distribute moderation stakes depending on your activity from 1 stake to 10 stakes. If you can not complete the task within the time given to you, we will assign a new translator. Approved translators have to join the Digipharm Translators Telegram group (link will be sent via pm). We are looking for Jr. Members or above.   Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s     Telegram Campaign    Join our Telegram channel and get 1 stake! Total bounty allocated will be divided to the number of participants. Putting “TipperEconomy.io” to your Telegram name earns you 20 stakes!  JOIN THROUGH: https://t.me/joinchat/HjnmdhAb4dOBxP8eaiNmoA   Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/wuZd3s
